txt.en: The drakes of Wyrmdelf have laid an enormous number of eggs, creating a threat that the Rohirrim might not be able to overcome.\n\nYou should destroy as many of the eggs as possible.
The drakes of Wyrmdelf have laid an enormous number of eggs, creating a threat that the Rohirrim might not be able to overcome.
You should cull the drake-horde by destroying their eggs
Drake-eggs can be found in nests throughout the Wyrmdelf.\n\nYou should destroy any drake-eggs you find in the Wyrmdelf.
